            The object of the clause is to open up trustee bodies to the prospect of remuneration under controlled terms. My guess is&#x2014;it seems common sense and certitude&#x2014;that there will be more of those cases in the future, unfortunately, than there have been in the past. But I shall leave it at that and I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
