        <q>Page 41, leave out lines 28 to 31 and insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>(12) Where&#x2014;</q>
        <ol>
        <li>(a) the charity trustees are notified by the Commission that it concurs with the resolution, or</li>
        <li>(b) the period of three months mentioned in subsection (10) above has elapsed without the Commission notifying them that it does not concur with the resolution,"</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0670P0-05645'>
