      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0670P0-05647'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050316_GCR_185' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 173 and 174 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0670P0-05648'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050316_GCR_186' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
